updates.update_content:
We have a little over one day left in the campaign, and we only need one new backer or a couple upgraded pledges to hit our goal, so I just wanted to let everyone know that they can add more cards to their pledge if they wish. One of the cool things about treasure cards is that you can create your own randomized treasure decks to draw from, which makes having more than one copy of each card a definite bonus. If you would like to increase your pledge to add additional packs of cards, go ahead and add the following amounts:
Arms & Armor: $10.00; 
Adventuring Gear: $10.00;
Gemstones: $4.00;
Blanks: $2.00;
